"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"a sneak peek\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"the polarizing cardboard beds\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ina July 22 TikTok,Daley vouched for the eco-friendly furniture's sturdiness, showing skeptical viewers evidence of its sound structure by knocking on the headboard and pulling at the bedpost.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2135115640487438e-37, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Daley\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"the eco-friendly furniture's sturdiness\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"skeptical viewers evidence\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"its sound structure\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"the headboard\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"the bedpost\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is cardboard,\\\" Tom explained to viewers.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then you have got the mattress and then this cardboard with the mattress on top with a mattress topper.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mattress\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"then this cardboard\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"the mattress\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1143}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"a mattress topper\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then, we get our own Paris '24 [comforter].\\\"\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [{\"beg