, \"to\": 3176}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think people, of course, after they finish competing, are enjoying themselves.\\\"\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Host countries began distributing condoms to athletes starting with France in 1992 during the Winter Olympics in Albertville.\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3355, \"end\": 3361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999286365376963, \"rank\": 6.406159147537513e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3400, \"end\": 3411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albertville\", \"score\": 0.999590490088694, \"rank\": 0.0004096776784091155, \"text\": \"Albertville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albertville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albertville\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Host countries\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3301}, {\"ngram\": \"condoms\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3340}, {\"ngram\": \"the Winter Olympics\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toSky News, an estimated 150,000 condoms were handed out at the Tokyo Games, and with pandemic-era restrictions being lifted for the Paris games, a reported 300,000 condoms will be available this year.\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3556, \"end\": 3561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998203748, \"rank\": 1.7940545997202927e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P